{"tid":1170573,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感] 6月9日出唔出黎 問你自己就得。","createTime":"2019-05-25T05:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T06:43:20.000Z","uid":13759,"like":63,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2328cb6f5438e2241ef3050986e03433762b0e48","tid":1170573,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"6月9日出黎唔出黎，反唔反對對逃犯條例，其實唔需要由連登仔話你聽有咩好定唔好，更加唔洗問你朋友同親人。<br />\n<br />\n大個仔啦，自己覺得呢樣野係啱嘅就去做，呢個唔係嘉年華會，就算無朋友陪你去，你都可以去。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有朋友話要返工不了，太熱不了，要排喜茶不了，都唔緊要。呢個係佢地嘅選擇。你可以嘗試話俾佢地聽你嘅睇法，去唔去由佢決定，但唔好奢望可以改變到佢地。<br />\n<br />\n人與人之間本身就有唔同價值觀，你可以選擇同邊種人做朋友，你更加可以選擇做你朋友唔會做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界太多人，思考過，如果你覺得啱就做，唔好太介意人地點睇。<br />\n<br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3346759ae6f12682718bd497ff57f55e79875c","tid":1170573,"uid":13759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9bcc6bea56fd4b6e4a0ba326ce53baa22733bd","tid":1170573,"uid":34213,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:28:58.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道"},{"pid":"50bdc74641e846ad5006b0f1f3485e07bfdf7228","tid":1170573,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820fc5311728e1768c8ee317e41aabee32411489","tid":1170573,"uid":255472,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"樓主好中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d59ff6f2724f90877e4bb4292017485f1466c1","tid":1170573,"uid":228244,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"rep